messages.message: I clicked on the first sample prompt of the Trust Chatbot (https://aihub.instabase.com/hub/apps/85f506f2-c7fb-4413-a2c7-68a7dc1d9d9e) and it responded with "I don't know". I think adding appropriate & tested sample prompts for this chatbot should help the user experience (e.g. the sample prompt about "a joke" doesn't seem fitting for a chatbot for security questions)
